{"tid":2450673,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"張致恒欠債6位數不知太太放負 雯雯：放棄都唔會帶埋兩個仔！","createTime":"2021-03-17T14:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T14:39:58.000Z","uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a719c17374f0f6a7038deddfdd9b17b9b3380b8a","tid":2450673,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2903791/90_1024.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2903791%2F90_1024.jpeg&h=c0f85814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張致恒（Steven）被爆負債累累，為怕債主臨門更一家著草搬屋避債，搞到舊居貼滿街招。據悉Steven欠下街數逾40萬，當中債主有馮鎵瀠（Naomi）和林盛斌，Naomi更公開追債。雖然Steven在事件曝光後網上發文向Naomi謝罪，太太雯雯亦指一家人沒有走佬避債，為還錢不惜而向財務公司借貸，請Naomi不要再騷擾她的家人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2900000/2903791/71_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2900000%2F2903791%2F71_600.jpg&h=37484494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於雯雯擔心老公和兩個兒子下壓力爆煲，不時在IG放負，「唔再生存，係咪先可以畀我哋平靜過？」財困問題未解決，昨晚（16/3）她再次在IG的限時動態中，以黑底白字寫著「就算絕路，我都會撐住兩個仔，要放棄，都唔會帶兩個仔！我相信我靠自己，一定可以撐住兩個仔！給自己少少鼓勵。」雖然雯雯說是給自己鼓勵，但不少網友看留言，尤其是「要放棄，都唔會帶兩個仔」，實在擔心她情緒出問題會否做出傻事？而傳媒即時聯絡Steven了解其妻狀況，他短訊回覆「我老婆有咩事啊？」當再傳雯雯的IG限時動態截圖給他看時，Steven則再沒回應。<br />\n<br />\nNaomi似乎不受雯雯「放負」這一套？後者昨晚出完post，時間啱啱好，Naomi 今日（17/3）也在自己IG限時動態表示︰「好漂亮的一段話啊！娶妻娶德不娶色，嫁人嫁心不嫁財，交友交心不交利。當面責罵那是友，背後亂叫那是狗！真正的好朋友，互損不會翻臉，疏遠不會猜疑，出錢不會計較，地位不分高低，成功毋須巴結，失敗不會離去。奮鬥的時候搭把手，迷茫的時候拉把手，開心的時候乾杯酒，難過的日子一起走&mdash;&mdash;致此生真正的朋友。」Naomi不著邊際的「回應」，是否衝著Steven一家而來？又係時候對號入座嘞！"},{"pid":"e60eb3df9eededee3389809c1ce4da8e0ae068e7","tid":2450673,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2903791/張致恒欠債6位數不知太太放負%20雯雯：放棄都唔會帶埋兩個仔！\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2903791%2F%E5%BC%B5%E8%87%B4%E6%81%92%E6%AC%A0%E5%82%B56%E4%BD%8D%E6%95%B8%E4%B8%8D%E7%9F%A5%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%AA%E6%94%BE%E8%B2%A0%2520%E9%9B%AF%E9%9B%AF%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E9%83%BD%E5%94%94%E6%9C%83%E5%B8%B6%E5%9F%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8B%E4%BB%94%EF%BC%81&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=cd49287e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2903791/張致恒欠債6位數不知太太放負%20雯雯：放棄都唔會帶埋兩個仔！</a>"},{"pid":"bdf88d3aeda0b1844c44f6f44fcfd101c524c958","tid":2450673,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72627ce2faee5ba25643e9b7143fa28d812b76d6","tid":2450673,"uid":126226,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"他短訊回覆「我老婆有咩事啊？」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b8a8cae277f3b7da3a869558cf3d34bc67baf8","tid":2450673,"uid":2300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:35:32.000Z","msg":"「做雞就是把自己的身體短期槓桿。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833aa98ca10921c2d77b906a51a357ba2c69e0e0","tid":2450673,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:36:16.000Z","msg":"六位數就要生要死<br />\n有無廢成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be07f3a4035a5c0dd84cdb42a2c34068d0595d2","tid":2450673,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T14:39:58.000Z","msg":"咁你做雞未 雯雯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建興好多位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}